languages.text: "Враг хитер и коварен. Вероятно, они следили за нами? Об этом непременно надо доложить губернатору!"
"The enemy is smart and cunning. Perhaps they were watching us? I must report this to the governor!"

languages.text: « L'ennemi est intelligent et rusé. Ils nous observaient peut-être. Je dois le signaler au gouverneur ! »
languages.original_text: "The enemy is smart and cunning. Perhaps they were watching us? I must report this to the governor!"

languages.text: “那些敌人很聪明、很狡猾，或许他们之前一直在监视我们？我必须向总督报告这件事情！”
languages.original_text: "The enemy is smart and cunning. Perhaps they were watching us? I must report this to the governor!"

traits.locale_text: “那些敌人很聪明、很狡猾，或许他们之前一直在监视我们？我必须向总督报告这件事情！”

languages.text: 「敵は賢く、狡猾だ。もしかしたら奴らは我々を監視していたのかもしれない。総督に報告しなければ！」
languages.original_text: "The enemy is smart and cunning. Perhaps they were watching us? I must report this to the governor!"

traits.locale_text: 「敵は賢く、狡猾だ。もしかしたら奴らは我々を監視していたのかもしれない。知事に報告しなければ！」

languages.text: «El enemigo es listo y astuto. ¿Quizás nos estaban observando? ¡Debo informar de esto al gobernador!».
languages.original_text: "The enemy is smart and cunning. Perhaps they were watching us? I must report this to the governor!"

languages.text: "Düşmanımız çok zeki, çok kurnaz. Acaba bizi mi izliyorlardı? Bunu valiye bildirmeliyim!"
